&lt;h5 id=&#34;12-回滚-deployment&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#12-回滚-deployment&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 1.2 回滚 Deployment&lt;/h5&gt;
